poma≈æu vam da se fokusirate na va≈æne stvari, dok se u isto vrijeme osjeƒáate kako kod kuƒáe. Pojednostavljeno a≈æuriranje Nemojte se gubiti izmeƒëu zaslona; ostanite na [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Jurica Zuanovic\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3964:\"<p>Nova WordPress inaƒçica 4.6, nazvana &#8220;Pepper&#8221; u ƒçast jazz bariton saksofonista Park Frederick ‚ÄúPepper‚Äù Adams III, dostupna je za preuzimanje i nadogradnju. Nove moguƒánosti i pobolj≈°anja u inaƒçici 4.6 poma≈æu vam da se fokusirate na va≈æne stvari, dok se u isto vrijeme osjeƒáate kako kod kuƒáe.</p>\n<p><iframe width=\'612\' height=\'344\' src=\'https://videopress.com/embed/GbdhpGF3?hd=1&amp;defaultLangCode=hr\' frameborder=\'0\' allowfullscreen></iframe><script src=\'https://v0.wordpress.com/js/next/videopress-iframe.js?m=1435166243\'></script></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>Pojednostavljeno a≈æuriranje</h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2016/08/streamlined-updates.png\" alt=\"Pobolj≈°ano ureƒëivanje\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" /></p>\n<p>Nemojte se gubiti izmeƒëu zaslona; ostanite na istom zaslonu dok a≈æurirate, instalirate i bri≈°ete va≈°e dodatke i teme.</p>\n<h2>Nativni fontovi</h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2016/08/native-fonts.png\" alt=\"Nativni fontovi\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" /></p>\n<p>WordPress nadzorna ploƒça sada koristi fontove koje imate, zbog ƒçega se stranice br≈æe uƒçitavaju i daje vam osjeƒáaj veƒá poznatog okru≈æenja, bez obzira koji ureƒëaj koristite.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2>Pobolj≈°ani ureƒëivaƒç</h2>\n<h3>Provjeravanje poveznica u retku</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2016/08/inline-link-checker.png\" alt=\"Provjera poveznica\" width=\"992\" height=\"595\" /></p>\n<p>Jeste li ikada sluƒçajno napravili poveznicu na https://wordpress.org/example.org? Sada WordPress automatski provjerava kako bi bili sigurni da niste.</p>\n<h3>Spa≈°avanje sadr≈æaja</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2016/08/content-recovery.png\" alt=\"Spa≈°avanje sadr≈æaja\" width=\"992\" height=\"595\" /></p>\n<p>Dok pi≈°ete, WordPress snima va≈° sadr≈æaj u pregledniku. Spa≈°avanje snimljenog sadr≈æaja je lak≈°e s WordPress 4.6.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2>Ispod haube</h2>\n<h3>Savjeti za resurse</h3>\n<p>Savjeti za resurse (Resource hints) poma≈æu preglednicima odluƒçiti koji resurs dohvatiti i unaprijed obraditi. WordPress 4.6 ih automatski dodaje za va≈°e stilove i skripte ƒçineƒái va≈°u web stranicu jo≈° br≈æom.</p>\n<h3>Robusni zahtjevi</h3>\n<p>HTTP API sada utjeƒçe na Requests library, pobolj≈°ava HTTP standardnu podr≈°ku i dodaje podr≈°ku za case-insensitive headers, paralelne HTTP zahtjeve i podr≈°ku za internacionalna imena domena.</p>\n<h3>WP_Term_Query i WP_Post_Type</h3>\n<p>Nova WP_Term_Query klasa dodaje fleksibilnost u informacije o pojmu upita (query term information), dok novi WP_Post_Type objekt ƒçini interakciju s tipovima objava vi≈°e predvidljivom.</p>\n<h3>Meta Registration API</h3>\n<p>Meta Registration API je pro≈°iren pa sada podr≈æava tipove, opise i REST API vidljivost.</p>\n<h3>Prijevodi na zahtijev</h3>\n<p>WordPress ƒáe od sada instalirati i koristiti najnovije jeziƒçne pakete za va≈°e dodatke i teme, ƒçim oni postanu dostupni od strane WordPress.org zajednice prevoditelja.</p>\n<h3>A≈æuriranja JavaScript zbirki</h3>\n<p>Masonry 3.3.2, imagesLoaded 3.2.0, MediaElement.js 2.22.0, TinyMCE 4.4.1, i Backbone.js 1.3.3 dolaze u paketu.</p>\n<h3>API-ji Prilagodnika za Postavke validacije i Obavijesti</h3>\n<p>Postavke sada imaju API za validaciju ograniƒçenja. Na sliƒçan naƒçin, kontrole Prilagodnika sada podr≈æavaju obavijesti koje se koriste za prikazivanje validacijski gre≈°aka.</p>\n<h3>Multisite, sada br≈æi neko ikada</h3>\n<p>Predmemorirani i obimni upiti web stranici (site queries) pobolj≈°avaju admin iskustvo na va≈°oj mre≈æi. Dodavanje WP_Site_Query i WP_Network_Query poma≈æe izgradnji naprednih upita s manje napora.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://hr.wordpress.org/releases/\">Preuzmite WordPress 4.6</a>, ili posjetite <strong>Nadzorna ploƒça ‚Üí Nadogradnje</strong> i a≈æurirajte svoju¬†instalaciju WordPressa.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://hr.wordpress.org/2016/08/19/wordpress-4-6/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"WordCamp Split 3. i 4 rujna 2016.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://hr.wordpress.org/2016/07/29/wordcamp-split-3-i-4-rujna-2016/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://hr.wordpress.org/2016/07/29/wordcamp-split-3-i-4-rujna-2016/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 29 Jul 2016 15:28:47 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Dogaƒëaji\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://hr.wordpress.org/?p=1116\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:390:\"Drugi WordCamp po redu u organizaciji hrvatske WordPress zajednice, odr≈æati ƒáe se od 3. &#8211; 4. rujna 2016. u Splitu, na Ekonomskom fakultetu. U petak 2. rujna, prije dva glavna konferencijska dana, biti ƒáe organizirane¬†besplatne radionice¬†za sve zainteresirane. Broj mjesta je ograniƒçen na 30 sudionika, ali u sluƒçaju velike zainteresiranosti, oni s kartama za WordCamp [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Jurica Zuanovic\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5200:\"<p>Drugi WordCamp po redu u organizaciji hrvatske WordPress zajednice, odr≈æati ƒáe se od <strong>3. &#8211; 4. rujna 2016. u Splitu, na Ekonomskom fakultetu</strong>. U <strong>petak 2. rujna</strong>, prije dva glavna konferencijska dana, biti ƒáe organizirane¬†<strong>besplatne radionice</strong>¬†za sve zainteresirane. Broj mjesta je ograniƒçen na 30 sudionika, ali u sluƒçaju velike zainteresiranosti, oni s kartama za WordCamp Split ƒáe imati prednost pohaƒëanja radionica. Ovdje se prijavite za pohaƒëanje <a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/schedule/\">WordCamp Split 2016 besplatnih radionica</a>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>12:05h¬†<strong>Kako da se va≈° korisnik osjeƒáa kao superheroj u 5 jednostavnih koraka</strong> &#8211;¬†<em>Aleksandar Savkoviƒá</em></li>\n<li>12:10h¬†<strong>Prikupljanje i vizualizacija podataka</strong> &#8211;¬†<em>Konrad Leon Toldy</em></li>\n<li>16:00h¬†<strong>The Art of Public Speaking</strong> &#8211;¬†<em>Luca Sartoni</em></li>\n<li>16:05h¬†<strong>Moj prvi WordPress plugin</strong> &#8211;¬†<em>Konrad Leon Toldy</em></li>\n<li>16:10h¬†<strong>(Uvod u) Upravljanje WordPress projektima</strong> &#8211;¬†<em>Kre≈°imir Konƒçiƒá</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Organizatori WordCampa Split u prodaju su pustili <strong>200 karata, po simboliƒçnoj cijenu od $20, ≈°to iznosi oko 130kn</strong>. S kartom dobivate osiguran ulaz na konferenciju, ruƒçak, goodise od sponzora, WordCamp Split majicu i ulaz na afterparty s ukljuƒçenim besplatnim piƒáem. Po≈°to je broj ulaznica ograniƒçen, po≈æurite se nabaviti svoju <a href=\"http://2016.split.wordcamp.org/tickets/\">ulaznicu za WordCamp Split</a>.</p>\n<p>Imati ƒáete priliku poslu≈°ati predavanja, i postaviti pitanja na≈°im predavaƒçima o sljedeƒáim temama:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/session/how-to-start-a-business-in-wordpress-a-codeable-story/\"><strong>Toma≈æ Zaman</strong> &#8211; <em>How to start a business in WordPress; a Codeable story</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/session/how-to-grow-your-business-by-producing-quality-blog-posts/\"><strong>Nevena Tomoviƒá</strong> &#8211; <em>How To Grow Your Business By Producing Quality Blog Posts?</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/session/using-wordpress-rest-api/\"><strong>Tomislav Leljak</strong> &#8211; <em>Using WordPress REST API</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/session/the-frustration-with-website-security/\"><strong>Jo≈°ko D≈æidiƒá</strong> &#8211; <em>The frustration with website security</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/session/team-up-for-wordpress-org-themes/\"><strong>Milan Ivanoviƒá</strong> &#8211; <em>Team up for WordPress.org Themes</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/session/kako-kvalitetno-prikazati-varijacije-proizvoda-savjeti-i-trikovi/\"><strong>Borko Liviƒá</strong> &#8211; <em>Kako kvalitetno prikazati varijacije proizvoda? (savjeti i trikovi)</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"Growth Methodologies in a Distributed Environment\"><strong>Luca Sartoni</strong> &#8211; <em>Growth Methodologies in a Distributed Environment</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/session/custom-url-structures-in-wordpress/\"><strong>Andrej ≈†imunaj</strong> &#8211; <em>Custom URL structures in WordPress</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/session/designing-a-brand/\"><strong>Natko Hasiƒá</strong> &#8211; <em>Designing a Brand</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/session/moving-the-design-process-to-the-browser/\"><strong>Lucijan Blagonic</strong> &#8211; <em>Moving the design process to the browser</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/session/related-posts-based-on-user-engagement/\"><strong>Emir Kurtoviƒá</strong> &#8211; <em>Related posts based on user engagement</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/session/end-design-revision-hell/\"><strong>Nela Dunato</strong> &#8211; <em>End Design Revision Hell</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/session/moving-forward-in-wordpress/\"><strong>Noel Tock</strong> &#8211; <em>Moving forward in WordPress</em></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Konferencijski dan zapoƒçinje u <strong>subotu 3. rujna u 8:00 sati</strong> s registracijom posjetitelja, a veƒá u 9:00 poƒçinje prvo predavanje. U 12:30 predviƒëena je stanka za ruƒçak, a u 17:30 je kraj konferencije, za vi≈°e informacija svakako pogledajte <a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/schedule/\">WordCamp Split konferencijski raspored</a>.</p>\n<p>U <strong>nedjelju 4. rujna</strong> biti ƒáe organiziran <strong>Contributor day, s poƒçetkom u 10:00 sati</strong>. Svi su pozvani da sudjeluju, bez obzira koliko je va≈°e znanje o WordPressu, jeste li programer ili ne. Biti ƒáe prisutni ljudi koji ƒáe vam pomoƒái da nauƒçite kako doprinijeti WordPressu.</p>\n<p>Doƒëite i podr≈æite <strong>WordPress i WordCamp Split</strong>. Ne propustite odliƒçna predavanja i priliku za networking. Karte se u prodaji po cijenu od 20 dolara (preraƒçunato oko 130 kn). Nemojte ƒçekati zadnji tren da biste rezervirali svoju kartu, jer se lako mo≈æe dogoditi da ostanete bez nje.</p>\n<p>Vidimo se u Split.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://hr.wordpress.org/2016/07/29/wordcamp-split-3-i-4-rujna-2016/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"2. WordPress Meetup Split\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://hr.wordpress.org/2016/07/14/2-wordpress-meetup-split/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://hr.wordpress.org/2016/07/14/2-wordpress-meetup-split/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 14 Jul 2016 14:42:16 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Dogaƒëaji\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://hr.wordpress.org/?p=1102\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:437:\"2. WordPress Meetup Split odr≈æati ƒáe se 21. srpnja 2016. s poƒçetkom u 17h ¬†na¬†Fakultetu elektrotehnike, strojarstva i brodogradnje, u uƒçionici A106. Na drugom splitskom meetupu¬†Ivan Blagdan ovom prilikom ƒáe priƒçati o razlozima, naƒçinima i ƒçestim problemima u implementaciji HTTPS protokola u WordPressu. Organizatori meetupa¬†osvrnuti ƒáe se¬†i na protekli¬†WordCamp Europe, odr≈æanom u Beƒçu 24-26.06.2016. Odr≈æati [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Jurica Zuanovic\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1341:\"<p><strong>2. WordPress Meetup Split</strong> odr≈æati ƒáe se 21. srpnja 2016. s poƒçetkom u 17h ¬†na¬†Fakultetu elektrotehnike, strojarstva i brodogradnje, u uƒçionici A106.</p>\n<p>Na drugom splitskom meetupu¬†Ivan Blagdan ovom prilikom ƒáe priƒçati o razlozima, naƒçinima i ƒçestim problemima u implementaciji HTTPS protokola u WordPressu. Organizatori meetupa¬†osvrnuti ƒáe se¬†i na protekli¬†WordCamp Europe, odr≈æanom u Beƒçu 24-26.06.2016. Odr≈æati ƒáe se i¬†Q&amp;A session na kojem mo≈æete postaviti pitanje o svemu ≈°to vas zanima vezano za WordPress a svi prisutni vam mogu dati odgovor na va≈°e pitanje. Na ovom meetupu takoƒëer ƒáe te moƒái saznati sve¬†informacije koje vas¬†zanimaju iz prve ruke, od samih organizatora WordCampa, Ivana Blagdana i Gorana ≈†eriƒáa, pogotovo ako ƒáe te biti volonter na <strong><a href=\"https://2016.split.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\">WordCamp Split 02-04.09.2016</a></strong>.</p>\n<p>Pridru≈æite nam se na zanimljivim i pouƒçnim predavanjima, upoznajte lokalnu zajednicu i predavaƒçe, i ne propustite priliku da popriƒçate o temama sa predavanja sa samim predavaƒçima :). <strong>Predavanja su besplatna, ali je prijava obavezna</strong> na¬†<a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/wordpress-croatia/events/232583667/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.meetup.com/wordpress-croatia/events/232583667/</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://hr.wordpress.org/2016/07/14/2-wordpress-meetup-split/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"h